===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-us-tardy.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Adjective===
'''tardy'''
#[[late|Late]]; [[overdue]] or [[delayed]].
#:''He yawned, then raised a '''tardy''' hand over his mouth.''

====Synonyms====
: [[belated]]
: [[long-delayed]]

====Usage notes====
*There is a suggestion of habitual lateness about the use of the word tardy. 
*More common in Commonwealth English
*Somewhat dated.

